<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>83</hymn_number>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zantim ah a liannganmi hla, Vawlei ah a rung thang, Vancungmi nih
 vawlei naih in an tingtang tumnak in, Vancung Siangpahrang Bawi sin in,
 Daihnak mi sin tum seh, Dai zirziar in vawlei a um, Vanmi hla thawng
 ngaih ah.

[V2]
 Vanrang aa hungmi khin an ra, An thla samh zual lo in, An zai tingtang
 lei partha bang en in aa zel chialmal, Leizur cungah an thla an zam,
 Vancung mithiang mi nih, Babel inn sa lungmawng rual sin, Vanmi zaihla an
 vel.

[V3]
 Sualnak phorhrit tang a ummi, Nannih leicung mi hna, Thadi le
 zaangbang harnak in chosang a kaimi hna, Cuan cio tuah u, lunglawmhnak
 caan, A tlung cang, ra tuah u, Lam pawng naidem tang i din in, Van hla
 sak thawng ngai u.

[V4]
 Ni le thla an liam lengmang ko, Profet hna chim chung bang. Kum cang
 aa mer lengmangmi cu, Sui chan a chuak te lai, Lei cungah daihnak a um
 lai, Harnak um ti loin, Vancung an hlasakmi kha, Mi nih an hun leh lai.</lyrics>
<title>ZANTIM DAI AH A RA CH83</title>
</song>